{"tid":2458881,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜濤點名多謝保錡被讚重情義","createTime":"2021-03-23T19:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T11:50:26.000Z","uid":85180,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"334ac505e38366d804a73fbeb6397f4cc777fcec","tid":2458881,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T19:47:33.000Z","msg":"姜濤點名多謝保錡被讚重情義<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2RE6TLp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2RE6TLp.jpg&h=3ac6b0f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n姜濤日前推出第七首個人單曲《Master Class》，他在社交網站撰文逐一感謝幕後功臣，包括填詞人黃偉文，「每一字句都寫中我的心聲，讓不善言辭的我藉此歌更好地表達自己的想法。」姜濤最後又感謝ERROR成員吳保錡，皆因保錡有份幫忙拍攝MV。<br />\n<br />\n  自從宣佈暫別幕前工作後，保錡一直沒有更新社交網，他亦罕有「上水」留言回覆姜濤說：「一直都會支持你，謝謝你對音樂的熱誠，期待你有更多有靈魂有說話的作品。」網友紛紛大讚姜濤重情義，沒有與保錡割席，也留言鼓勵保錡，相當有愛！"},{"pid":"7a7db3bb481669dee08262a5f185af418ffa6f29","tid":2458881,"uid":85180,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T19:51:53.000Z","msg":"恭喜保錡有viutv 一哥撐，復出毫無疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b3be0dede35728ea35d1446456592fd39da20a","tid":2458881,"uid":209773,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7a7db3bb481669dee08262a5f185af418ffa6f29","tid":2458881,"uid":85180,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T19:51:53.000Z","msg":"恭喜保錡有viutv 一哥撐，復出毫無疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T19:55:09.000Z","msg":"viu一哥係錡哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31688c2ed0425870157c757703b356bcdbc2035","tid":2458881,"uid":85180,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16b3be0dede35728ea35d1446456592fd39da20a","tid":2458881,"uid":209773,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7a7db3bb481669dee08262a5f185af418ffa6f29","tid":2458881,"uid":85180,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T19:51:53.000Z","msg":"恭喜保錡有viutv 一哥撐，復出毫無疑問<img src=\"/assets/fac